\nabla F=(f_x, f_y).
\nabla F_{(1,3)}=\frac{f_x+3f_y}{\sqrt10}=\frac{-2}{\sqrt5}
\nabla F_{(5,5)}=\frac{5f_x+5f_y}{5\sqrt2}=\frac{f_x+f_y}{\sqrt2}=1
f_y=\frac{-3}{\sqrt2}
f_x=\frac{5}{\sqrt2}
